This repository contains a script to automatically **extend a disk partition, resize the physical volume (PV), logical volume (LV), and the filesystem** on Linux systems using LVM.

The main script included is:

- `extensio-disk.sh` â€“ Automatically grows a partition and its corresponding LVM logical volume.

